===============================================================
A simple pod catcher written for webOS using the enyo framework
===============================================================

This software is a simple pod catcher trageted for devices
running HP's webOS. It features a intuitive three column layout
and basic Playback functionality. Multiple feeds are supported.
Feeds can be searched while playing. Podcast description is
displayed, supporting also HTML content.

